name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 8, in Lanzhou, Gansu, some netizens reported that the foundation of the first phase of Evergrande Landscape City shops collapsed and the houses were in a suspended state.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 6, in Nanchang, Jiangxi, a woman live-broadcasted near the Wanshou Palace, reporting by real name the chairman of Jiangxi Fengcheng Fucheng Real Estate, Huang Yuancheng, for poisoning and murder, bribery and tax evasion, and involvement in organized crime and other crimes.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 7, a netizen filmed a video of a courier sorting station at work, in which the workers were sorting packages as quickly as machines.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 8, the Hong Kong Department of Justice won the appeal and the court issued a temporary injunction order "Glory to Hong Kong"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 8, in Cangzhou, Hebei, Lujie Environmental Protection Technology Co., Ltd. owed the cleaners seven months’ salary, and the elderly came to the town government to demand their wages and defend their rights.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 7, Anhui Huaibei Capital Experimental Primary School distributed a survey to parents, saying that in order to eliminate the competitive mentality among students, it asked parents whether they supported the purchase of anti-comparison shoes at 600 yuan a pair.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: May 8 (Release), Beijing. Tangshan’s Beijing Office staff openly snatched a petitioner’s ID card at the station square and ran away.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On May 8, someone jumped off a building at Deji Plaza in Nanjing Xinjiekou.
In the suicide note of the deceased in his circle of friends, he revealed that he had lost tens of millions of yuan during the epidemic, and was unwilling to bow to fate under severe mental stress and severe depression. So after the epidemic was over, he decided to move the store to Shilin Home Furnishing and renovate it for reopening.
As a result, he never expected that the store was sublet to other merchants during the renovation stage, and he got into a dispute and was asked to move the store. After investing 1.8 million yuan, he lost all his money. In the end, he had to choose to end his life.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 8, in Cangzhou, Hebei, the Rongsheng Huayucheng property had delayed delivery for more than a year. The owners went to the local Housing and Construction Bureau to seek an explanation.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 8, in Guangzhou, Guangdong, villagers from Hengsha Village came to the Dasha Subdistrict Office to ask for temporary relocation fees.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 8, in Jing County, Hebei Province, the Taihuali Jingfuyuan real estate project was left unfinished. Owners held up banners in front of the county government to protest their rights and knelt down to ask to see the county party secretary.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 8, a Fuzhou native who came to the United States through an online connection posted a video saying that he asked the embassy staff about reissuing his passport. The other party said that without the documents of legal entry, the passport could not be reissued and he could only provide a certificate of return to the country.
